ased on tile coordinates, and one based on a bounding box. Classes that implement this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"protocol must implement one, and only one of the methods. Methods on this protocol will not be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"called on main thread, they will be called on the caller’s "},{"code":"requestQueue","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesourcedatasource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNStyle":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNStyle","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNStyle","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy object for the current map style."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnstyle"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSource"}],"title":"MLNShapeSource","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON"},{"type":"text","text":" code. A shape source is added to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can update a shape source by setting its "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shape"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"URL"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNComputedShapeSource":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MLNComputedShapeSource","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlncomputedshapesource","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNComputedShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"one tile at a time, to be shown on the map on demand. You implement a class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conforming to the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNComputedShapeSourceDataSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol that returns"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"instances of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", then add a computed shape source to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the computed shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"source."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSourceOptionClustered":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClustered"}],"title":"MLNShapeSourceOptionClustered","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSourceOptionClustered","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSNumber"},{"type":"text","text":" object containing a Boolean enabling or disabling clustering."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"shape"},{"type":"text","text":" property contains point shapes, setting this option to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" clusters the points by radius into groups. The default value is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesourceoptionclustered"},"doc://or